le=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: currentcolor none medium !important; font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">Bước 2: Cho l&aacute; bồ c&ocirc;ng anh v&agrave; ch&egrave; xanh, hoa quế v&agrave;o h&atilde;m trong 5&nbsp; &ndash; 10 ph&uacute;t.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none !important; font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: currentcolor none medium !important; font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">Bước 3: Lọc lấy nước tr&agrave; v&agrave; uống khi c&ograve;n n&oacute;ng.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; outline: none !important; color: #333333; font-family: Montserrat, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: currentcolor none medium !important; font-weight: 400; font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\">Tr&agrave; bồ c&ocirc;ng anh ch&egrave; xanh lợi tiểu, chống vi&ecirc;m,giải độc rất tốt. Đay l&agrave; loại tr&agrave; ph&ugrave; hợp với nguwoif dễ bị nhiễm tr&ugrave;ng hoặc vi&ecirc;m răng miệng, h&ocirc;i miệng. Tr&agrave; được bỏ th&ecirc;m hoa quế c&oacute; m&ugrave;i thơm dịu, ngọt ấm. N&ecirc;n h&oacute;a quế sẽ điều chỉnh vị lạnh của bồ c&ocirc;ng anh, uống nhiều sẽ giảm bớt sự bốc hỏa, n&oacute;ng trong người.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none !important; display: block; color: #333333; font-family: Montserrat, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-4685 aligncenter\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; outline: none !important; border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; height: auto; clear: both; display: block;\" src=\"https://jarvis.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/tra-bo-cong-anh-ket-hop-voi-tra-xanh-hoa-que.jpg\" alt=\"Tr&agrave; bồ c&ocirc;ng anh kết hợp với tr&agrave; xanh hoa quế\" width=\"600\" height=\"402\" /></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; outline: none !important; color: #333333; font-family: Montserrat, FontAwesome, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #000000;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; outline: none !important;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px;